# QuizDsl

Gema para la representaciÃ³n natural de un examen en DSL

## Installation

Add this line to your application's Gemfile:

```ruby
gem 'quiz_dsl'
```

And then execute:

    $ bundle

Or install it yourself as:

    $ gem install quiz_dsl

## Usage

@quiz = Quiz.new("test"){ |e|
		e.question "Pregunta 1",
		e.right => "Answer 1" ,
		e.wrong => "Answer2"
		}

